 excess of zeal 
 in the meantime gavroche had had an adventure 
 gavroche after having conscientiously stoned the lantern in the rue du chaume entered the rue des and not seeing even a cat there he thought the opportunity a good one to strike up all the song of which he was capable 
 his march far from being retarded by his singing was accelerated by it 
 he began to sow along the sleeping or terrified houses these incendiary couplets 
 
