 dites donc le colonel gerard est ici he asked 
 tell me is colonel gerard here 
 mot repeated the sentinel barring the way and not replying 
 quand un officier fait sa ronde les sentinelles ne demandent pas le mot cried dolokhov suddenly flaring up and riding straight at the sentinel je vous demande si le colonel est ici 
 when an officer is making his round sentinels ask him for the password i am asking you if the colonel is here 
