 harry ron hermione and ginny were spending all of their time together the beautiful weather seemed to mock them harry could imagine how it would have been if dumbledore had not died and they had had this time together at the very end of the year examinations finished the pressure of homework lifted and hour by hour he put off saying the thing that he knew he must say doing what he knew it was right to do because it was too hard to forgo his best source of comfort 
 
